      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以data5是Infra_LoadBalancer作为输入数据，data5a是Infra_IngressController，data5b是Infra_WorkerNode，这三个都是inputData类型对吧？",
