      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "理解了，样式不同。那op3c的输入是data3和data3c，分别是Infra_WorkerNode和Infra_IngressController，也都是inputData类型？",
